snippet.title: Raven Fortress Dungeon - First Room - Tidewoken
snippet.description:
I had some fun doing the Raven Fortress dungeon today and decided to record some gameplay footage meanwhile. Let me know if you prefer videos with commentary or just game sound.

Tidewoken is a co-op & PvP focused multiplayer turn-based tactics game with thousands of possible character builds. Choose out of 4 classes, 192 skills, and 30+ perks.

Follow & Wishlist the game on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1135220/Tidewoken/

And join our Discord Server for news & discussions:
https://discord.gg/hcR2m2R

This video is showing pre-release footage and does not resemble a fully released game.
